            Experience the joy and excitement of a Mickey Mouse birthday party!<br /> From fun games to delightful decorations, we create unforgettable memories<br /> for your little ones.</p>
            <br /><br />
    </div>

    <div class="gallery fade-in">
        <div class="image-box fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;"><img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/camlEl1KnbVSXI9VVXqYJOrVwjRZ8wBT_lL0aYPOw0c.jpg" alt="Mickey Mouse Birthday Image 1"></div>
        <div class="image-box fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;"><img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/zbI9qAfV0_UI6H_9_uCMqWFLq6NNcC4mCiyjOBg8HLk.jpg" alt="Mickey Mouse Birthday Image 2"></div>
        <div class="image-box fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;"><img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/UkJIXSm44EU7R3O-XouhrCGoyq20phIaGBffZoGyU6s.jpg" alt="Mickey Mouse Birthday Image 3"></div>
        <div class="image-box fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;"><img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/a1aa/image/a0HR1jhuuY3TwTy8P37iOBDdJrKEYoHjlYT4p77NNfA.jpg" alt="Mickey Mouse Birthday Image 4"></div>
